Repentance & Holiness Info App is a simple, easy to use android application that has consolidated all the Altars of the LORD in one place to allow you your locate your respective Altar with ease.

In addition to finding the location, you can also get the contact details of the Senior pastor of your specific church as well as listening to the end time radio Station, JESUS IS LORD RADIO, in the application.

It also contains the urgent messages of the GLORIOUS GOD OF ISRAEL brought to the earth by the MIGHTIEST PROPHETS OF THE LORD
A testimony from HEAVEN through the TWO MOST DREADFUL WITNESSES OF REVELATIONS 11.

Prepare the Way of the LORD. The Messiah is coming
descriptionShort: An android app to help you find Altars, Teachings, Prophecies of the LORD.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
-Updated Healings section to allow scroling
-Updated radio to play smoothly on the background
-Updated User interface
-It now supports up to android 14
-Few Bug fixes
